  "body": "👋  Hello guys !\r\n\r\nI'm facing an issue with some methods in the `debug_` namespace, when the result is an error. The returned result does not follow the JSON standard, since a 'null' is added directly at the end of the `result` field. Here are some examples:\r\n\r\n# debug_traceTransaction\r\nRequest:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": 2.0,\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"method\": \"debug_traceTransaction\",\r\n    \"params\": [\"0x7a6dea3226bb4d640250473708a427ad2418e8b0a1c42fb6d3e3da69a75f0026\"]\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nResponse: \r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"result\":nullnull,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32000,\r\n        \"message\": \"missing block number\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nExpected response:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32000,\r\n        \"message\": \"missing block number\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n# debug_traceCall\r\nRequest:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": 2.0,\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"method\": \"debug_traceCall\",\r\n    \"params\": [\r\n        {\r\n            \"to\": \"0xdef171fe48cf0115b1d80b88dc8eab59176fee57\",\r\n            \"data\": \"\",\r\n            \"gas\": \"0x2d5b0\",\r\n            \"maxFeePerGas\": \"0x5d21dba00\",\r\n            \"maxPriorityFeePerGas\": \"0x42294180\",\r\n            \"nonce\": \"0x1\",\r\n            \"from\": \"0x3f87926741eca0d162184e17fa78b954c080c594\",\r\n            \"value\": \"0x34ac080e80e94c\"\r\n        },\r\n        \"latest\"\r\n    ]\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nResponse:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"result\": {\r\n        \"structLogs\": []\r\n    }null,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32000,\r\n        \"message\": \"tracing failed: fee cap less than block base fee: address 0x3f87926741eca0D162184e17fa78B954C080c594, gasFeeCap: 25000000000 baseFee: 51821831514\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nExpected response:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32000,\r\n        \"message\": \"tracing failed: fee cap less than block base fee: address 0x3f87926741eca0D162184e17fa78B954C080c594, gasFeeCap: 25000000000 baseFee: 51821831514\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThanks in advance !",
